#. Tag: title
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "OPIS"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Kbackup is a program that lets you back up any directories or files. It uses "
"an easy to use directory tree to select the things to back up and lets you "
"save your settings in \"profile\" files. These are simple textfiles "
"containing definitions for directories and files to be included or excluded "
"from the backup process."
msgstr ""
"Kbackup je program, ki omogoča varnostno kopiranje vseh imenikov ali "
"datotek. Za izbiro stvari za varnostno kopiranje uporablja enostavno drevo "
"imenikov in omogoča shranjevanje nastavitev v datotekah \"profilov\". To so "
"preproste besedilne datoteke, ki vsebujejo definicije imenikov in datotek, "
"ki se vključijo ali izključijo iz postopka varnostnega kopiranja."

#. Tag: title
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "OPTIONS"
msgstr "MOŽNOSTI"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "-v, --version"
msgstr "-v, --version"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays version information."
msgstr "Prikaže informacije o različici."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "-h, --help"
msgstr "-h, --help"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays help on commandline options."
msgstr "Prikaže pomoč za možnosti ukazne vrstice."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "--help-all"
msgstr "--help-all"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays help including Qt specific options."
msgstr "Prikaže pomoč, vključno s posebnimi možnostmi Qt."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "--help-all --qmljsdebugger <replaceable>value</replaceable>"
msgstr "--help-all --qmljsdebugger <replaceable>vrednost</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Activates the QML/JS debugger with a specified port. The value must be of "
"format port:1234[,block]. \"block\" makes the application wait for a "
"connection."
msgstr ""
"Vključi razhroščevalnik QML/JS z določenimi vrati. Vrednost mora biti v "
"obliki port:1234[,block]. \"block\" povzroči, da aplikacija počaka na "
"povezavo."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "--script <replaceable>file</replaceable>"
msgstr "--script <replaceable>file</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "Script to run after finishing one archive slice."
msgstr "Skript za zagon po dokončanju ene arhivske rezine."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "--auto <replaceable>profile</replaceable>"
msgstr "--auto <replaceable>profile</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Automatically run the backup with the given profile and terminate when done."
msgstr ""
"Samodejno zažene varnostno kopijo z danim profilom in jo zaključi, ko je "
"končana."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid "--autobg <replaceable>profile</replaceable>"
msgstr "--autobg <replaceable>profil</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Automatically run the backup with the given profile in the background "
"(without showing a window) and terminate when done."
msgstr ""
"Samodejno zažene varnostno kopijo z danim profilom v ozadju (brez prikaza "
"okna) in jo zaključi, ko je končana."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid "--verbose <replaceable>profile</replaceable>"
msgstr "--verbose <replaceable>profil</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In autobg mode be verbose and print every single filename during backup."
msgstr ""
"V načinu autobg je med varnostnim kopiranjem beseden in izpiše vsako "
"posamezno ime datoteke."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "--forceFull"
msgstr "--forceFull"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In auto/autobg mode force the backup to be a full backup instead of acting "
"on the profile settings."
msgstr ""
"V načinu auto/autobg prisili varnostno kopijo, da je popolna varnostna "
"kopija, namesto da bi delovala na podlagi nastavitev profila."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid "--author"
msgstr "--author"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show author information."
msgstr "Pokaži informacije o avtorju."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid "--license"
msgstr "--license"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show license information."
msgstr "Pokaži informacije o licenci."

#. Tag: option
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid "--desktopfile <replaceable>file</replaceable>"
msgstr "--desktopfile <replaceable>datoteka</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kbackup.1.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "The base file name of the desktop entry for this application."
msgstr "Ime osnovne datoteke vnosa namizja za to aplikacijo."

